data.text:
FENTON Lena E., age 94, of Okc, Ok., was born March 25, 1899 in Cazenovia township, Woodford County, Ill. to Peter and Elizabeth Bachman.

Lena passed over on July 25, 1993. She retired as a nursery attendant for the Church of God, where she was a member. She was preceded in death by two sons, Bob Fenton in 1986 and Ronald Fenton in 1993. Survivors include her daughter, Naydene Perkins and son-in-law, Tom; seven grandchildren and three great grandchildren.

Lena will be missed as a wonderful mother, grandmother and friend.

Graveside services are 10:00 a.m. Thursday, July 29, 1993 at Resthaven Memory Gardens. BIOG: NAME:
